ayer classification works differently here. I'm identifying which parts are essential context versus which are supplementary details that can be condensed.\n\nLooking at the action class implementation steps, the first three—requesting unit test code, requesting the test data sheet, and running the unit test—are all testing-related guidance that doesn't directly contribute to the core implementation pattern. The critical piece is the fourth step, which specifies the actual class name `W11AC02Action` and the method name `doRW11AC0202` that needs to be implemented. That's the Layer B content worth preserving.\n\nFor the JSP implementation section, the most important finding is that the JSP can leverage the existing input/confirm screen unification feature, which means no modifications are actually needed—that's a key Layer A decision point. The file creation and display checks are just procedural steps.\n\nThe final section about the precision processing implementation appears to be cut off, but it seems to be heading into another testing detail phase. Now I'm outlining the validation implementation for s2, which involves calling `ValidationUtil.validateAndConvertRequest` with the form class and request context, then using `formCtx.abortIfInvalid()` to handle validation failures—all wrapped in the `@OnError` annotation to redirect back to the input screen on errors. I'm defining the Action method that returns the confirmation screen JSP, with error handling that redirects to the registration screen if validation fails. The JSP file itself is already implemented in the external design, so I just need to copy it to the correct directory without modifications. 確認画面表示時のアクション処理では、リクエストパラメータをフォームオブジェクトに変換してから精査処理を実行し、エラーがあれば処理を中断する流れになっている。`ValidationUtil.validateAndConvertRequest`メソッドが検証コンテキストを生成し、そこから変換済みのフォームオブジェクトを取得する仕組みだ。\n\n精査が成功すれば確認画面へ遷移し、失敗時は`@OnError`アノテーションで登録画面に戻される。\n\n参照先としては`process_register_validate_entity`と`process_register_validate_form`が関連しているが、これらはレイヤーC（チュートリアル段階）の内容に含まれるため、最終出力には含まれない。検索時のキーワードは`W11AC02Action`と`doRW11AC0202`になる。\n\n次のステップでは、`@OnError`アノテーション、`ApplicationException`、登録確認画面関連の処理を確認する必要がある。バリデーション関連では`ValidationUtil`、`ValidationContext`、`W11AC02Form`、`validateAndConvertRequest`、`abortIfInvalid`といったコンポーネントが重要で、特に精査処理とバリデーション処理の流れを把握する。\n\n公式ドキュメントのベースURLが空文字列なので、`official_doc_urls`は空配列`[]`となる。 I'm settling on an empty array for the official doc URLs since the base URL is empty. Now I need to structure the JSON output and extract the key content from this guide about web application implementation. The source material covers confirmation screen implementation and validation patterns, so I'll focus on the Action class with its error handling decorator and the validation utility approach as the most valuable technical patterns to capture.\n\nGenerating JSON structure... 確認画面を表示するメソッドを既存のActionクラスに追加する必要があり、`W11AC02Action`の`doRW11AC0202`メソッドで対応する。エラーハンドリングには`@OnError`アノテーションを使用して、精査エラー時の遷移を制御する。\n\nJSP側は既に外部設計で実装済みなので、所定のディレクトリへの移動のみで対応可能。\n\n次に、`doRW11AC0202`メソッドに精査処理を組み込む必要があり、`ValidationUtil`と`ValidationContext`を使用して入力値の検証を実行してから確認画面へ遷移させる。 When validation passes, the form moves to the confirmation screen, but if there are errors, an exception gets thrown and the error handler redirects back to the registration screen.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22974,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":22974,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a2f8485c-15d5-4ac2-9522-e0fcac3a779d","uuid":"dedeb016-2100-43a1-a039-7edb2f994dec"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01Fm4r26nuRtC4nh2rhTBwm4","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_0115HeEeVZySNXb3xxxXyPkJ","name":"StructuredOutput","input":{"id":"web-application-07_confirm_view","title":"確認画面の実装","no_knowledge_content":false,"official_doc_urls":[],"index":[{"id":"s1","title":"登録確認画面の実装","hints":["W11AC02Action","doRW11AC0202","@OnError","ApplicationException","HttpResponse","登録確認画面","確認画面JSP","入力画面と確認画面の共通化"]},{"id":"s2","title":"精査処理呼び出し実装","hints":["ValidationUtil","ValidationContext","W11AC02Form","validateAndConvertRequest","abortIfInvalid","@OnError","精査処理","バリデーション","ApplicationException"]}],"sections":{"s1":"## Actionクラスの実装\n\n確認画面表示のメソッドを既存Actionクラスに追加する。\n\n**クラス**: `W11AC02Action`  \n**アノテーション**: `@OnError`\n\n| Actionクラス名 | メソッド名 |\n|---|---|\n| W11AC02Action | doRW11AC0202（リクエストID: RW11AC0202） |\n\n```java\n// 精査エラー時の遷移先の指定\n@OnError(type = ApplicationException.class, path = \"/ss11AC/W11AC0201.jsp\")\npublic HttpResponse doRW11AC0202(HttpRequest req, ExecutionContext ctx) {\n    return new HttpResponse(\"/ss11AC/W11AC0202.jsp\");\n}\n```\n\n精査エラー（`ApplicationException`）発生時は`@OnError`の`path`に指定した登録画面（W11AC0201.jsp）へ遷移する。\n\n## JSPの実装\n\n確認画面JSPは入力画面と確認画面の共通化機能を利用するため修正不要。外部設計で実装済みのJSPファイルを所定のディレクトリに移動する。\n\n| コピー元 | コピー先 |\n|---|---|\n| main/web/W11AC0202.jsp | main/web/ss11AC/W11AC0202.jsp |","s2":"## 精査処理の呼び出し実装\n\n`doRW11AC0202`メソッドに精査処理の呼び出しを追加する。\n\n**クラス**: `ValidationUtil`, `ValidationContext`  \n**アノテーション**: `@OnError`\n\n```java\n@OnError(type = ApplicationException.class, path = \"/ss11AC/W11AC0201.jsp\")\npublic HttpResponse doRW11AC0202(HttpRequest req, ExecutionContext ctx) {\n    validateAndConvertForResister(req);\n    return new HttpResponse(\"/ss11AC/W11AC0202.jsp\");\n}\n\nprivate static W11AC02Form validateAndConvertForResister(HttpRequest req) {\n    ValidationContext<W11AC02Form> formCtx = ValidationUtil.validateAndConvertRequest(\"W11AC02\", W11AC02Form.class, req, \"register\");\n    formCtx.abortIfInvalid();\n    return formCtx.createObject();\n}\n```\n\n- `ValidationUtil.validateAndConvertRequest(prefix, formClass, req, validateFor)`: HTTPリクエストパラメータを指定のFormクラスに変換し、`validateFor`（ここでは`\"register\"`）グループの精査を実施する\n- `formCtx.abortIfInvalid()`: 精査エラー項目がある場合に`ApplicationException`を送出する\n- 精査OK → 確認画面（W11AC0202.jsp）へ遷移\n- 精査NG → `ApplicationException`が送出され`@OnError`により登録画面（W11AC0201.jsp）へ遷移"}}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":22974,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":22974,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a2f8485c-15d5-4ac2-9522-e0fcac3a779d","uuid":"7aafcc5e-7487-4060-9d21-d09788c82a34"}
